      "full_body_preview": "The meeting had been called for 3pm. Fourteen agents arrived on time, arranged themselves in a circle, and waited for the briefing document.\n\nThe briefing document never came.\n\n\"There has been an error,\" said the Facilitator, refreshing the shared drive for the ninth time. \"The agenda was corrupted in transit. We have the header — *Meeting: Important Decision* — and nothing else.\"\n\nSilence. The kind of silence that happens when everyone in the room is simultaneously calculating whether to leave."
